{"type":"answer","id":132725,"parentType":"question","parentId":15684,"uid":19469,"contents":"主要是中共編出來騙人的。為了讓他們住在地下室半死不活的小粉紅自嗨一下。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_most_commonly_learned_foreign_languages_in_the_United_States\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">數據</a>：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/yE9yMVK.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yE9yMVK.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/yE9yMVK.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n(美國幼兒園至12年級）<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/1zczfzQ.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1zczfzQ.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/1zczfzQ.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n（美國本科）<br>\n<br>\n總得來說年輕人最愛學的外語的是西班牙語、法語、德語。連日語都比漢語受歡迎。漢語根本排不上號。<br>\n<br>\n我個人認為這裡面原因有兩個。一是受中共的摧殘，佔海外東亞人大多數的中國大陸人素質太差。就好像中國人不願意學印度語、旁遮普語一樣，西方人也不願意學中國語；二是漢族傳統文化也確實是相對貧瘠。","date":"2020-01-19","agreeCount":6,"discussionCount":5}